<concept id="concept_3413BBD173324104B42FB714974CABE7" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Managing Marketplaces</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>This chapter describes</p>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>How to create marketplaces. </li>
                    <li>How to change the owner of a marketplace.</li>
                    <li>How to delete a marketplace.</li>
                    <li>How to configure marketplaces.</li>
                    <li>How to update the search index.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p>For details on administrating and customizing your own or tenant-specific marketplaces, refer to the <i>Marketplace Owner's Guide</i>.</p>
            <p>Use the <ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> reporting facilities, for example, to retrieve information on the services published to your marketplace. For details, see chapter <xref
                    href="../Reports/c_Reports.xml"/>.</p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
